# .gitignore — The Ambered Jack site repo.
# Anything matched here is NEVER tracked, pushed to GitHub, or deployed.
# NOTE: each rule must be alone on its line — git has no inline comments.

# --- PRIVATE material (must never leave the machine) ---
# client/agency source assets, logos, photos:
/assets/
# internal retainer / strategy docs:
/retainer/

# --- BACKUPS (frozen rollback zips — never delete, never commit) ---
/website-deploys/

# --- Regenerable junk ---
node_modules/
.impeccable/
playwright-report/
test-results/
.playwright/

# --- Tooling that physically lives INSIDE the served site/ folder ---
# Kept locally for dev/testing, but excluded so Cloudflare's site/ output
# serves ONLY website files (no tooling reachable by URL).
/site/tests/
/site/tools/
/site/netlify.toml
/site/package.json
/site/package-lock.json
/site/playwright.config.js
/site/.gitignore
/site/README-DEPLOY.md
/site/CLAUDE-CODE-BRIEF.md
/site/TESTING.md

# --- OS / editor clutter ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
